text: Carl Personne (11 May 1888 - 4 October 1976) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1976 deaths Category:People from Mjölby Municipality Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
